{"title":"Inside theme+MathJax","date":"2020-03-17T15:14:13.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 17, 2020","L":"03/17/2020","MM-DD":"03-17"},"link":"2020/03/17/Inside theme+MathJax","tags":["website"],"updated":"2020-03-17T15:48:37.346Z","content":"<p>The original Inside theme can’t render the mathmatical formula written by latex code normally. So I want to add MathJax plugin to render it.</p>\n<p>Someone has developed a plugin named “hexo-filter-mathjax-ssr”. I will add it to my website.</p>\n<h1 id=\"Installation\">Installation<a href=\"2020/03/17/Inside theme+MathJax#Installation\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-filter-mathjax-ssr --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>If your internet speed was poor, maybe you can refer to “Migration of Hexo+Github Pages” in the root.</p>\n<h1 id=\"Config\">Config<a href=\"2020/03/17/Inside theme+MathJax#Config\"></a></h1><p>hexo/_config.yml</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mathjax:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  inlineQuote: [&apos;<svg xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" width=\"2.016ex\" height=\"2.843ex\" style=\"vertical-align: -0.671ex;\" viewbox=\"0 -934.9 868.1 1223.9\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-labelledby=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">\n<title id=\"MathJax-SVG-1-Title\">', '</title>\n<defs aria-hidden=\"true\">\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-2032\" d=\"M79 43Q73 43 52 49T30 61Q30 68 85 293T146 528Q161 560 198 560Q218 560 240 545T262 501Q262 496 260 486Q259 479 173 263T84 45T79 43Z\"/>\n<path stroke-width=\"1\" id=\"E1-MJMAIN-2C\" d=\"M78 35T78 60T94 103T137 121Q165 121 187 96T210 8Q210 -27 201 -60T180 -117T154 -158T130 -185T117 -194Q113 -194 104 -185T95 -172Q95 -168 106 -156T131 -126T157 -76T173 -3V9L172 8Q170 7 167 6T161 3T152 1T140 0Q113 0 96 17Z\"/>\n</defs>\n<g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"matrix(1 0 0 -1 0 0)\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n <use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMAIN-2032\" x=\"0\" y=\"583\"/>\n<g transform=\"translate(294,0)\">\n <use xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMAIN-2C\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\"/>\n <use transform=\"scale(0.707)\" xlink:href=\"#E1-MJMAIN-2032\" x=\"393\" y=\"583\"/>\n</g>\n</g>\n</svg>&apos;]</span><br><span class=\"line\">  blockQuote: [&apos;MATHJAX-SSR-0&apos;]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>done!</p>\n<h3 id=\"Reference\"><em>Reference</em><a href=\"2020/03/17/Inside theme+MathJax#Reference\"></a></h3><p><a href=\"https://blog.oniuo.com/post/math-jax-ssr-example#cauchys-integral-formula\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://blog.oniuo.com/post/math-jax-ssr-example#cauchys-integral-formula</a></p>\n","next":{"title":"法院判决书","link":"2020/03/15/聪明的小耗子"},"plink":"https://thswind.github.io/2020/03/17/Inside theme+MathJax/","toc":[{"title":"Installation","id":"Installation","index":"1"},{"title":"Config","id":"Config","index":"2"}],"reward":true}